    "It brings the opportunity to move forward from the mass education system to personalized and adaptive learning methods.",
    "It can facilitate data analysis and visualization in academic course delivery and training.",
    "Therefore, it would lead us to appealing training for both students and teachers.",
    "On the other hand, students are normally technology-lovers, and using new technologies, such as GAI, will engage them in educational activities.",
